node.text: Eric brought in his gorgeous 2016 Arancio Argos Huracan in for the SheepeyRace treatment. We added our Stage 1 SR 888-R kit to this car and made a very fun and streetable 800 hp. We couldn't be happier with the way this build turned out and neither can Eric.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by sheepeyrace on September 17, 2021. May be an image of car.

node.text:
Heads up we’ve got two of the cleanest white super cars going out! First we have Charlotte, NC’s very own @ccm.luis ‘s with a Mac-daddy and full billet gear-set that’s putting down 1,400+ HP as well  @alierquesada ‘s Huracan which is heading back to Miami, Florida equipped with our stage 1 kit! Don’t strain your neck when you see this land planes fly by 🚀

Also, vlog out now!! 

#sheepeyrace #sheepeybuilt #sheepeybrand #ttgang
